
This code was developed for the DLP-RFID1 RFID tag reader.
It targets the Linux operating system, but should be portable
pending its dependencies.

The application should likely be run as root, or rather,
with access to USB devices.

The code in this directory depends on the following libraries:

pthreads
libftdi
libcurl
libavahi-client

use
make all
to build client and sample server.

avahi-publish
is a sample Avahi service advertiser, advertising the following service
_rfid-srv._tcp
